  "Asia Pacific (Osaka)"
  "Asia Pacific (Singapore)"
  "Asia Pacific (Sydney)"
  "Canada (Central)"
  "Europe (Frankfurt)"
  "Europe (Ireland)"
  "Europe (London)"
